metadata.name: Depressed Whale #8531
metadata.description:
Depressed Whales: Neon Collection

Depressed Whales are manifestation of sadness and trouble that dwell inside us. They represent pain and suffering we experience, and also show our struggle and effort in reaching out for hope. Each of them are unique and no one Depressed Whales are the same.

Hopefully, you'll be able to find the Depressed Whale that empathize with your sadness, and guide you to a place where serenity resides.

Edition 1 of 1
